'''奶油塔 '''是一种加拿大小型[[挞|挞]]类[[糕点|糕点]]，是典型的加拿大甜点。奶油塔的内馅由黄油、糖、糖浆、鸡蛋和干果组成，这些材料倒进塔皮里，烤到表皮酥脆，内馅半凝固。<ref name=great>{{Cite episode |title=What makes a great butter tart? |series=[[Morningside_(radio_program)|Morningside]] |credits= Presenter:[[Peter_Gzowski|Peter Gzowski]] Guests:Max Burns, Marion Kane, Charles Pachter |network=[[CBC_Radio|CBC Radio]] |station=[[CBC_Radio_One|CBC Radio One]] |city=[[Moose_Jaw|Moose Jaw]] |airdate=1991-12-05}}</ref>很多家庭有自己独特的奶油塔做法，因此不同糕点店做的奶油塔，在馅料和软硬程度上有很大不同。<ref name=>{{citation |title=Better butter tarts |journal=The Ottawa Citizen |date=2006-10-26 |url=http://www.canada.com/topics/lifestyle/food/story.html?id=be2adf75-3134-4a2d-97b2-280c9155d9c2 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110140939/http://www.canada.com/topics/lifestyle/food/story.html?id=be2adf75-3134-4a2d-97b2-280c9155d9c2 |archivedate=2012-11-10 |accessdate=2012-07-11 }}</ref>

一般情况下，英裔加拿大家庭的奶油塔包括黄油、 糖和鸡蛋，类似于法裔加拿大人的糖派或简易版的美国[[胡桃派|胡桃派]]。奶油塔和胡桃派最主要的区别是，胡桃派含有大量玉米糖浆，因此口感更粘稠。传统奶油塔一定含有葡萄干，另外可添加核桃和胡桃等坚果。不过纯粹主义者认为奶油塔只能有葡萄干。<ref name=SS/>

其他附加成分可以包括黑醋栗、[[椰|椰]]子、[[海枣|海枣]]、[[焦糖|焦糖]]、巧克力碎屑、[[花生酱|花生酱]]、[[糖枫|枫糖浆]]或浓茶.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thesweetoven.com/buttertarts.htm |title=Sweet Oven bakery, Butter tart flavours |access-date=2012-07-11 |archive-date=2012-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120915015758/http://www.thesweetoven.com/buttertarts.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 骆驼塔是深受游客喜爱的加拿大顶级甜点之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.canada-visa-online.org/zh-CN/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%B8%E5%AE%A2%E5%96%9C%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9C%E7%82%B9/ |title="加拿大最受欢迎的甜点。" |access-date=2022-02-22 |archive-date=2021-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029080543/https://www.canada-visa-online.org/zh-CN/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%B8%E5%AE%A2%E5%96%9C%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9C%E7%82%B9/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

